snippet.title: Forgotten Playland - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Forgotten Playland is an upcoming free-to-play social party game. Set in an isolated and abandoned attic, a group of small plush toy characters known as Plushies have been left to their own devices.

► Visit our website: https://forgottenplayland.com/
► Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/ForgotPlayland
► Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/ForgottenPlayland

Want to learn more about Beam?
